{"id":"0337fa0b-6948-4417-950a-275d210e7390","title":"1481/08/22","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"d0d7c312-7615-49d0-87b4-0c0530c6e6dc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"With regard to this custom, I am pleased to add that on the 15th October, 1547, a decree was published by the Otto di Guardia e di Balia (the Eight), on the observance of the fetes, forbidding any work to be done on these days, and the shops to keep open, with certain exceptions, amongst which is the following: \u0022And four apothecaries\u0027 shops, to be drawn by lot among the Arte (Guild), may remain open all day; the others may sell from 21 in the evening onwards\u0022 (5 p.m.).","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2df36b61-e7d1-4e21-b9b7-031ab61f0b24","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":28,"end":28,"value":"5d9cbd12-a35b-4b1c-9130-36c6786145b2","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"284563cf-4284-4cd6-9c9a-e1d4a44b49c5","type":"codex/time-reference","start":60,"end":77,"value":"8cd154e0-c397-48ad-b09b-34bd561309d9","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"aef99263-8dae-4c48-bf44-0152a1aac6dc","type":"style/superscript","start":62,"end":63,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"925587a5-d65b-45cf-89cf-4f66ca5891b4","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":110,"end":135,"value":"13a95965-81df-493b-9d58-a17e1f3733be","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6c659abb-1342-4657-944b-238604ba2a1d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":142,"end":146,"value":"13a95965-81df-493b-9d58-a17e1f3733be","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"50a77a9f-4e2c-4bcb-9538-700b0ad22af2","type":"style/italics","start":373,"end":376,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]}]}